longBusinessSummary: Lucara Diamond Corp., a diamond mining company, engages in the development and operation of diamond properties in Africa. It holds a 100% interest in the Karowe mine located in Botswana. The company also operates Clara Platform, a digital sales platform for rough diamonds. The company was formerly known as Bannockburn Resources Limited and changed its name to Lucara Diamond Corp. in August 2007. Lucara Diamond Corp. was incorporated in 1981 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
